            <additions>
              <p/>
              <list>
                <item xml:id="addition1" n="1">
                  <locus from="181" to="183"/>
                  <p>Foll. 183 and 181 are paper leaves, both slightly stained and torn, containing
                    part of the first epistle of S. John, according to the Pěshīttā version, viz.
                    ch. iv. 13—v. 12, written in an elegant hand of the xivth cent.</p>
                  <p>
